{"tid":1599740,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"列根號南海遭中國七艦包圍","createTime":"2019-09-28T07:22:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T15:28:10.000Z","uid":25558,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"0789b30b5f8c32f80c2625237b4b0d0eb8fee128","tid":1599740,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T07:22:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20190927/SUWNDGZXQYPHJCJI4YM326GU7A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20190927%2FSUWNDGZXQYPHJCJI4YM326GU7A%2F&d=%2F9qUFN9YWCJnPZyZgWzOjwqYqcROYCvJBJmaWwU8HGA%3D&h=dbe851f9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20190927%2FSUWNDGZXQYPHJCJI4YM326GU7A%2F&h=8fff3020\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20190927/SUWNDGZXQYPHJCJI4YM326GU7A/</a><br />\n<br />\n列根號南海遭中國七艦包圍<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/7yIrVfqWrfUe4xdOd2kXYonq4N0=/190x126/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/WB5R3BBWQLHHIYVOU74LQDFZH4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2F7yIrVfqWrfUe4xdOd2kXYonq4N0%3D%2F190x126%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FWB5R3BBWQLHHIYVOU74LQDFZH4.jpg&h=293f01b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖為美國列根號航母。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n中美關係緊張之際，外媒報道美國航空母艦列根號日前穿越南海水域時，周圍出現多艘中國軍艦。中國網民近日披露衞星照片指，「列根號」周邊至少有七艘解放軍軍艦環伺，美軍隨之派出一架RC-135和一架P-8A戰機支援。<br />\n<br />\n據報道，「列根號」本月從日本橫須賀基地駛出，9月23日駛經南海時，遭解放軍軍艦包圍。有中國軍迷在微博指，「據最新衞星圖顯示，目前美國列根號航母在南海疑被中方至少七艘軍艦包圍 ！另外，列根號被圍困時曾請求派機增援，結果美軍派出一架RC-135偵察機和一架P-8A反潛機救援」。<br />\n<br />\n中國國防部發言人任國強26日在記者會答應稱，堅決反對美國航母編隊到南海炫耀武力，並指軍隊認真履行使命，捍衞國家主權與安全。等於間接承認事件；唯不談細節。另據台軍方披露，26日中午東海上空一架美軍MC-130J沿台海中線由北向南飛行，解放軍曾派戰機監控。這是8月29日以來，美軍第二次派MC-130J型偵察機飛行台灣海峽。<br />\n<br />\n中央社/台灣蘋果新聞網"},{"pid":"de8477f67a696d5bdd1f33b03f510be7dc58abe0","tid":1599740,"uid":132827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T07:22:44.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"382ebb2be6ff669ae61acfe8fcbdae0ec742c50a","tid":1599740,"uid":134571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T07:22:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b30f0a78e99c3d3c7bbeda67c3594256f90b6392","tid":1599740,"uid":210612,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T07:23:24.000Z","msg":"北洋水師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n定遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 鎮遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"293628693e866cbd4b7719cc872a2fa0df224c76","tid":1599740,"uid":149534,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T07:24:36.000Z","msg":"Cuban missile crisis 2.0"},{"pid":"f7ab81ef18106ff949e65fdd6664af8a07c9fab9","tid":1599740,"uid":43428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T07:24:37.000Z","msg":"唔係得個圍字  要捍衛南海要出接出手<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3851167f8ad05361e34f1d767483890fd7b8a9b","tid":1599740,"uid":33336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T07:25:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20190927/SUWNDGZXQYPHJCJI4YM326GU7A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20190927%2FSUWNDGZXQYPHJCJI4YM326GU7A%2F&d=%2F9qUFN9YWCJnPZyZgWzOjwqYqcROYCvJBJmaWwU8HGA%3D&h=dbe851f9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20190927%2FSUWNDGZXQYPHJCJI4YM326GU7A%2F&h=8fff3020\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20190927/SUWNDGZXQYPHJCJI4YM326GU7A/</a><br />\n<br />\n列根號南海遭中國七艦包圍<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.c